<br>
Get a Paladin, grouped up with a mage. Have the pally DA, and run into Traks lair pulling him to the back of his lair.  Around your position one.. but you can pull him even further. Count off 8 seconds and have the Mage start Coh'ing the Paladin. Pally gets coh'd to safety, and Trak is safely tucked away in his room. The prot pull is simple after that and you saved your raid a ton of time instead of waiting for him to move on his own to spot 1 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <br>
<br>
I have used this method on two different occasions and it worked like a charm. Personally I dont believe the pally trusted me enough to actually try it.. lol. <br>
