<br>
Just get Trak stuck in the hall/cave near the setup spot (I'll let you figure how to do that) and kill him there.<br>
<br>
Then after Trak is dead, you go up and kill the rest of the lair.. prot, jumppy, and all.<br>
<br>
<br>
Just hope Trak doesn't get off a gate or you'll have to rush the whole lair anyway.  <br>
<br>
<br>
Trak is an easy kill so with 30+ people you should be able to kill him before he gets that gate off.<br>
<br>
Good technique to have incase your monk blows the pull and you &quot;accidentally&quot; get Trak stuck in hall.<br>
